stimulusHtml:
Capture and paste a procedure from your program that you developed during the administration of this task that implements an algorithm used in your program.

  • This procedure must contain and use one or more parameters that have an effect on the functionality of the procedure.

Provide a written response that:

(Approx. 200 words, exclusive of program code)

  • describes two calls to the selected procedure, where each call passes different arguments that cause a different segment of code in the algorithm to execute,
• describes what condition(s) is being tested by each call to the procedure, and
• identifies the result of each call.
